{
  "info": {
    "name": "CarPool — Driver API (Trivazo)",
    "description": "**Driver app — Postman**\n\n**Images / files:** binary files are **never** inside raw JSON. Send them as **multipart** fields: `license_doc`, `vehicle_image`, `profile_image` (same names as register). After upload, the **JSON response** has public URLs on `driver`: `license_doc_url`, `profile_image_url`, `vehicle_image_url`. Customer avatar is `driver.user.image_full_url` (from store `users`).\n\n1. Set `base_url`, `customer_phone`, `customer_password`.\n2. **Customer login** → `auth_token`.\n3. **Driver Register** — multipart + Bearer; response `{ status, message, driver }` with URLs above + nested `user` — no top-level `token`.\n4. **Driver login** — `{ status, token, driver }`.\n5. **Update profile** — JSON text only: **PUT**. With files: **POST** multipart (same URL). **GET profile** returns same URL fields.\n6. Admin verifies driver before **Create route** (`is_verified`).\n\nSee `CarPool-API.postman_collection.json` for examples.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://192.168.1.53:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "auth_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "customer_phone", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "customer_password", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "driver_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "route_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "driver_route_departure_at", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0 — Customer signup & public driver",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Vehicle categories (list)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/vehicle-categories"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Customer login (same account as driver)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('auth_token', j.token); }",
                  "if (j.user && j.user.phone) { pm.collectionVariables.set('customer_phone', j.user.phone); }",
                  "// Use same credentials for Driver Login after register."
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email_or_phone\": \"{{customer_phone}}\",\n  \"country_code\": \"+91\",\n  \"password\": \"{{customer_password}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
            "description": "Must succeed before Driver Register. Set `customer_phone` + `customer_password` variables to a registered store user."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Driver Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.driver && j.driver.id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('driver_id', String(j.driver.id));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "gender", "value": "male", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "vehicle_category_id", "value": "1", "description": "From GET vehicle-categories (active id)", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "vehicle_number", "value": "MH-01-AB-1234", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "vehicle_model", "value": "Maruti Swift", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "vehicle_color", "value": "White", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "vehicle_capacity", "value": "4", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "license_number", "value": "DL-2024-001", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "license_doc", "type": "file", "src": "" },
                { "key": "vehicle_image", "type": "file", "src": "" },
                { "key": "profile_image", "type": "file", "src": "", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/register",
            "description": "Vehicle type: send **either** `vehicle_category_id` or **`vehicle_category_name`** (e.g. `Sedan`). If both sent, **id wins**.\n\n**Response JSON:** `{ \"status\": true, \"message\": \"...\", \"driver\": { ... , \"user\": { \"id\", \"name\", \"f_name\", \"l_name\", \"email\", \"phone\", \"country_code\", \"image_full_url\" } } }` — no `token` in body."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Driver Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.token) { pm.collectionVariables.set('auth_token', j.token); }",
                  "if (j.driver && j.driver.id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('driver_id', String(j.driver.id)); }"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{customer_phone}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{customer_password}}\",\n  \"fcm_token\": \"optional_fcm_token\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/login",
            "description": "Same phone + password as **customer** (`users`). **Response:** `{ \"status\": true, \"token\": \"<Passport>\", \"driver\": { ... , \"user\": { ... } } }`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Search trips (passenger-style search)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/routes/search?origin_lat=28.6139&origin_lng=77.2090&destination_lat=28.5355&destination_lng=77.3910&date=2026-05-15&seats=1&radius_km=10&limit=15",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "carpool", "routes", "search"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "origin_lat", "value": "28.6139" },
                { "key": "origin_lng", "value": "77.2090" },
                { "key": "destination_lat", "value": "28.5355" },
                { "key": "destination_lng", "value": "77.3910" },
                { "key": "date", "value": "2026-05-15" },
                { "key": "seats", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "radius_km", "value": "10" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "15" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Driver public profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/{{driver_id}}/profile"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1 — Driver auth (Bearer)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get profile",
          "description": "**GET** `.../driver/profile`. **Response:** `{ \"status\": true, \"driver\": { ... , \"user\": { \"id\", \"name\", \"f_name\", \"l_name\", \"email\", \"phone\", \"country_code\", \"image_full_url\" } } }`.",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/profile"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update profile (JSON, PUT)",
          "description": "**PUT** — **Body must be raw JSON only.** In Postman do **not** switch this tab to **form-data** — with PUT, multipart is often **empty on the server** (nothing saves; you may still see an old `driver` object).\n\n**Request JSON keys (all optional):** `name`, `country_code`, `email`, `gender`, `vehicle_number`, `vehicle_model`, `vehicle_color`, `vehicle_capacity`, `license_number`, `fcm_token`, `is_online`, plus **`vehicle_category_id`** OR **`vehicle_category_name`** OR **`vehicle_type`** (same as category label from GET vehicle-categories, e.g. `Sedan`). Also **`license_doc` / `vehicle_image` / `profile_image`** as **`null`** in JSON = placeholders only; real files → **POST multipart**.\n\n**Response JSON** includes file URLs on `driver`: `license_doc_url`, `profile_image_url`, `vehicle_image_url`, plus nested `user` with `image_full_url`. Open **Example Response** on this request (or the POST multipart request).",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Test Driver Updated\",\n  \"country_code\": \"+91\",\n  \"email\": \"optional@driver.com\",\n  \"gender\": \"male\",\n  \"vehicle_type\": \"Sedan\",\n  \"vehicle_color\": \"Silver\",\n  \"vehicle_model\": \"Maruti Swift\",\n  \"vehicle_number\": \"MH-01-AB-1234\",\n  \"vehicle_capacity\": 4,\n  \"license_number\": \"DL-2024-001\",\n  \"fcm_token\": \"device_token_here\",\n  \"is_online\": true,\n  \"license_doc\": null,\n  \"vehicle_image\": null,\n  \"profile_image\": null\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/profile"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 — JSON with image URLs after text update (example)",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "PUT",
                "header": [],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "" },
                "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/profile"
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Profile updated successfully.\",\n  \"driver\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Test Driver Updated\",\n    \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n    \"country_code\": \"+91\",\n    \"email\": \"optional@driver.com\",\n    \"gender\": \"male\",\n    \"license_number\": \"DL-2024-001\",\n    \"license_doc_url\": \"http://localhost/storage/carpool/drivers/docs/doc.pdf\",\n    \"profile_image_url\": \"http://localhost/storage/carpool/drivers/photos/face.jpg\",\n    \"vehicle_category_id\": 1,\n    \"vehicle_type\": \"Sedan\",\n    \"vehicle_category\": { \"id\": 1, \"name\": \"Sedan\" },\n    \"vehicle_number\": \"MH-01-AB-1234\",\n    \"vehicle_model\": \"Maruti Swift\",\n    \"vehicle_color\": \"Silver\",\n    \"vehicle_capacity\": 4,\n    \"vehicle_image_url\": \"http://localhost/storage/carpool/drivers/vehicles/car.jpg\",\n    \"status\": \"active\",\n    \"is_verified\": true,\n    \"is_online\": true,\n    \"rating\": 4.8,\n    \"total_completed_rides\": 12,\n    \"wallet\": {\n      \"available_balance\": 0,\n      \"pending_balance\": 0,\n      \"total_earned\": 0,\n      \"total_withdrawn\": 0\n    },\n    \"user\": {\n      \"id\": 42,\n      \"name\": \"Test Driver Updated\",\n      \"f_name\": \"Test\",\n      \"l_name\": \"Driver\",\n      \"email\": \"optional@driver.com\",\n      \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n      \"country_code\": \"+91\",\n      \"image_full_url\": null\n    }\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Update profile with images (POST multipart)",
          "description": "**POST** `{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/profile` — **multipart/form-data**.\n\n**File parts (optional, any combination):**\n| Field | Rules |\n|-------|--------|\n| `license_doc` | file: pdf, jpg, jpeg, png; max 5120 KB |\n| `vehicle_image` | image: jpg, jpeg, png; max 3072 KB |\n| `profile_image` | image: jpg, jpeg, png; max 2048 KB |\n\n**Text parts (optional, same as PUT):** `name`, `country_code`, `email`, `gender`, `vehicle_category_id`, `vehicle_category_name`, **`vehicle_type`** (same as category label, e.g. `Sedan`), `vehicle_number`, `vehicle_model`, `vehicle_color`, `vehicle_capacity`, `license_number`, `fcm_token`, `is_online` (use `0`/`1` or `true`/`false` as strings if needed).\n\nDo **not** set `Content-Type` manually — Postman adds boundary.\n\n**Response** is JSON (see saved example below): `status`, `message`, `driver` with **`license_doc_url`**, **`profile_image_url`**, **`vehicle_image_url`**, **`user.image_full_url`**.",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "name", "value": "Test Driver", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "vehicle_color", "value": "Blue", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "is_online", "value": "1", "type": "text" },
                { "key": "license_doc", "type": "file", "src": "", "description": "pdf/jpg/png max 5MB" },
                { "key": "vehicle_image", "type": "file", "src": "", "description": "jpg/png max 3MB" },
                { "key": "profile_image", "type": "file", "src": "", "description": "jpg/png max 2MB" }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/profile"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 — JSON with image URLs (example)",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [],
                "body": { "mode": "formdata", "formdata": [] },
                "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/profile"
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"status\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Profile updated successfully.\",\n  \"driver\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Test Driver\",\n    \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n    \"country_code\": \"+91\",\n    \"email\": \"driver@example.com\",\n    \"gender\": \"male\",\n    \"license_number\": \"DL-2024-001\",\n    \"license_doc_url\": \"http://localhost/storage/carpool/drivers/docs/example.pdf\",\n    \"profile_image_url\": \"http://localhost/storage/carpool/drivers/photos/example.jpg\",\n    \"vehicle_category_id\": 1,\n    \"vehicle_type\": \"Sedan\",\n    \"vehicle_category\": { \"id\": 1, \"name\": \"Sedan\" },\n    \"vehicle_number\": \"MH-01-AB-1234\",\n    \"vehicle_model\": \"Maruti Swift\",\n    \"vehicle_color\": \"Blue\",\n    \"vehicle_capacity\": 4,\n    \"vehicle_image_url\": \"http://localhost/storage/carpool/drivers/vehicles/example.jpg\",\n    \"status\": \"active\",\n    \"is_verified\": true,\n    \"is_online\": true,\n    \"rating\": 4.8,\n    \"total_completed_rides\": 12,\n    \"wallet\": {\n      \"available_balance\": 1500.5,\n      \"pending_balance\": 0,\n      \"total_earned\": 5000,\n      \"total_withdrawn\": 1000\n    },\n    \"user\": {\n      \"id\": 42,\n      \"name\": \"Test Driver\",\n      \"f_name\": \"Test\",\n      \"l_name\": \"Driver\",\n      \"email\": \"driver@example.com\",\n      \"phone\": \"9876543210\",\n      \"country_code\": \"+91\",\n      \"image_full_url\": null\n    }\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Push live location",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"lat\": 28.6139,\n  \"lng\": 77.2090\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/location"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/logout"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2 — Wallet",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Wallet balance",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/wallet"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Transactions",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/wallet/transactions?limit=20",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "carpool", "driver", "wallet", "transactions"],
              "query": [{ "key": "limit", "value": "20" }]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Request withdrawal",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"amount\": 100,\n  \"account_details\": {\n    \"bank_name\": \"Example Bank\",\n    \"account_number\": \"1234567890\",\n    \"account_holder\": \"Test Driver\",\n    \"ifsc\": \"EXMP0001234\"\n  }\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/wallet/withdraw"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List withdrawals",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/wallet/withdrawals?status=all&limit=15",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "carpool", "driver", "wallet", "withdrawals"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "all" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "15" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3 — My routes (rides)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create route (ride)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var d = new Date();",
                  "d.setHours(d.getHours() + 2);",
                  "var pad = function(x){ return x < 10 ? '0'+x : ''+x; };",
                  "var s = d.getFullYear()+'-'+pad(d.getMonth()+1)+'-'+pad(d.getDate())+' '+pad(d.getHours())+':'+pad(d.getMinutes())+':00';",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('driver_route_departure_at', s);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.route && j.route.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('route_id', String(j.route.id));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"origin_name\": \"Connaught Place, New Delhi\",\n  \"origin_lat\": 28.6304,\n  \"origin_lng\": 77.2177,\n  \"destination_name\": \"Noida Sector 18\",\n  \"destination_lat\": 28.5706,\n  \"destination_lng\": 77.3212,\n  \"waypoints\": [],\n  \"ride_type\": \"scheduled\",\n  \"departure_at\": \"{{driver_route_departure_at}}\",\n  \"total_seats\": 3,\n  \"price_per_seat\": 150,\n  \"currency\": \"INR\",\n  \"estimated_duration_min\": 60,\n  \"estimated_distance_km\": 25,\n  \"note\": \"AC ride\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/my-routes",
            "description": "403 if driver `is_verified` is false — set verified in admin."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List my routes",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/my-routes?status=all&limit=15",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "carpool", "driver", "my-routes"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "all" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "15" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get route detail",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/my-routes/{{route_id}}"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Depart (start ride)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/my-routes/{{route_id}}/depart"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Complete ride",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/my-routes/{{route_id}}/complete"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Cancel route (no confirmed bookings)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{auth_token}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/carpool/driver/my-routes/{{route_id}}"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
